WEBVTT

02:00:31.065 --> 02:00:33.025
And if that does not shatter them...

02:00:33.234 --> 02:00:35.945
...and I am allowed a little peace
from foolish questions...

02:00:36.111 --> 02:00:39.573
...I will try to find the opening words.

02:00:40.032 --> 02:00:43.126
(GANDALF SPEAKS IN ELVISH
AND DWARVISH)

02:00:43.127 --> 02:00:45.127
Gate of elves...

02:00:46.631 --> 02:00:49.131
...listen to my word..

02:00:49.627 --> 02:00:51.827
...threshold of dwarves...
